Test programs.

setup: 
-----
start sysrepod and import oplink yang data model.

oplk_device.c - read sysrepo data store.
---------------------------------------

  options:
  -d, get device info;
  -p, get port info;
  -a, get edfa info;
  -o, get ocm info;
  -wf, get waveplan;

oplk_agent.c - config device.
----------------------------
  config device.
  add/dele connections:
      ./oplk_aent conn add <chnl_numb>
      ./oplk_agent conn del <chnl_numb>

  set port and channel target power
      ./oplk_agent power port <value>
      ./oplk_agent power chan <value>

  set waveplan
      ./oplk_agent waveplan all 
      ./oplk_agent waveplan chan <chan_number>

oplk_agent_alarm.c - listen to alarm posted by csm.
--------------------------------------------------

oplk_of_conifg.c - read OF config data model.
--------------------------------------------
